---
import CallToAction from './CallToAction.astro'
import ExternalLink from './ExternalLink.astro'
import Logo from './Logo.astro'

/**
 * Footer Component
 *
 * @description A component that displays the footer of the website
 */
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear()
const linkedinUrl = "https://www.linkedin.com/company/enejota-projects/"
const substackUrl = "https://codingpit.substack.com/"
const githubUrl = "https://github.com/Coding-Pit-Dev"
---

<footer>
  <section class="py-20">
    <h2 class="sr-only">Footer</h2>
    <div class="container grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <Logo loading="lazy" />
        <p class="leading-[1.75]">
          Consejo: prueba siempre la compatibilidad con lectores de pantalla. Pulsa <kbd>⌘</kbd> + <kbd>F5</kbd> para iniciar VoiceOver o <kbd>Win</kbd> + <kbd>Ctrl</kbd> + <kbd>Enter</kbd> para Narrator.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Contacto</h3>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <li><ExternalLink href={linkedinUrl}>Linkedin</ExternalLink></li>
          <li><ExternalLink href={substackUrl}>Substack</ExternalLink></li>
          <li><ExternalLink href={githubUrl}>Github</ExternalLink></li>
          <li><a href="/contacto">Formulario de contacto</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Servicios</h3>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <li><a href="/proyectos/apps">Desarrollo de apps</a></li>
          <li><a href="/formacion/cursos">Cursos</a></li>
          <li><a href="/formacion/mentorias">Mentorías</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="py-8">
    <div class="container flex flex-col gap-4 md:flex-row md:justify-between items-center">
      <p>
        &copy; {currentYear} - Coding Pit Web made with <a href="https://astro.build/">Astro</a>.
      </p>
      <div class="footer-social flex gap-4 items-center">
        <a href={linkedinUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="LinkedIn">
          <svg width="28" height="28" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.761 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.239-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-10h3v10zm-1.5-11.268c-.966 0-1.75-.784-1.75-1.75s.784-1.75 1.75-1.75 1.75.784 1.75 1.75-.784 1.75-1.75 1.75zm13.5 11.268h-3v-5.604c0-1.337-.026-3.063-1.868-3.063-1.868 0-2.154 1.459-2.154 2.968v5.699h-3v-10h2.881v1.367h.041c.401-.761 1.379-1.563 2.841-1.563 3.039 0 3.6 2.001 3.6 4.601v5.595z"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href={substackUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Substack">
          <svg width="28" height="28" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 32 32"><path d="M4 6.667h24v2.667H4zm0 5.333h24v2.667H4zm0 5.333h24v8H4z"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="https://medium.com/@juanjecilla" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Medium">
          <svg width="28" height="28" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M2.01 6.845c.007-.14-.04-.277-.133-.382l-1.6-1.92v-.28h4.978l3.85 8.44 3.38-8.44h4.78v.28l-1.37 1.31c-.118.09-.175.237-.15.38v10.98c-.025.143.032.29.15.38l1.34 1.31v.28h-6.78v-.28l1.39-1.35c.137-.137.137-.177.137-.38v-8.82l-3.87 10.53h-.52l-4.51-10.53v7.09c-.037.27.053.543.24.74l1.81 2.2v.28h-5.16v-.28l1.81-2.2c.185-.197.27-.47.23-.74z"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href={githubUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="GitHub">
          <svg width="28" height="28" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 .297c-6.63 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.303 3.438 9.8 8.205 11.385.6.113.82-.258.82-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.415-4.033-1.415-.546-1.387-1.333-1.757-1.333-1.757-1.089-.745.084-.729.084-.729 1.205.084 1.84 1.236 1.84 1.236 1.07 1.834 2.809 1.304 3.495.997.108-.775.418-1.305.762-1.605-2.665-.305-5.466-1.334-5.466-5.93 0-1.31.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.523.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.873.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.803 5.624-5.475 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.218.694.825.576C20.565 22.092 24 17.592 24 12.297c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      <p>
        Basado en el trabajo de <a href="https://github.com/markteekman">Mark Teekman</a> y su plantilla de <a href="https://github.com/incluud/accessible-astro-starter" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Astro</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</footer>

<style>
  section {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color-subtle);
  }
</style>
